snippet.title: Smash 4 Melee HD Mod - Beta Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Melee HD Mod [Name has since been changed] dev team has released the beta to the public. This version includes wavedashing, L-cancelling, crouch cancelling, and the same physics as melee.

Please consider subscribing as we begin to bring you more content in the full release (coming after feedback and once we finish things!)

Download in the Discord server:
Discord: https://discord.gg/pwW3Ygk

Twitter: https://twitter.com/MeleeHD_Mod

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCaW0OGdHLXVseaom0lR-YAA

Email: Smash4meleehdmod@gmail.com

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Melee_HD/

Trailer by user 'Raw Input' in our discord.
Song used : The Prototypes - Rocket Guns Blazin' (Crissy Criss + Malux + Erb N Dub Remix)
